186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4752x2673+0+438/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F01%2F51%2Febe98c5e41d8aa31592025092f5a%2F186071607-spencerhenderson-canadagoose.jpg" class="img" alt="A flock of Canada Geese. " loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 A flock of Canada Geese in the water.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Spencer Henderson                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;After beginning a birding journey, 21-year-old Spencer Henderson slowly convinced his friends to join him in his hobby. It was going according to plan until his girlfriend spotted a Canada Goose before he did. Then everyone who started this new hobby saw the bird except him. After searching for what felt like ages for the goose, he found more than 20 of them one day on the trail. "I was so relieved and ended up getting my favorite photo that I have taken," Henderson said. This photo is his favorite because it shows that hard work pays off.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Henderson's tip:&lt;/strong&gt; "Just be patient and don't be afraid to come back another day. Sometimes the shot just doesn't work out, or the birds aren't there, and there is nothing we can do about that. Coming back with a fresh head and some new ideas can make all the difference."&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-82585" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 3000;         --source-height: 1688;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1688+0+873/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fac%2F3c%2F85377f3b4b5097c32bc845e51e17%2F186071607-20250208-111044.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1688+0+873/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fac%2F3c%2F85377f3b4b5097c32bc845e51e17%2F186071607-20250208-111044.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1688+0+873/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fac%2F3c%2F85377f3b4b5097c32bc845e51e17%2F186071607-20250208-111044.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1688+0+873/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fac%2F3c%2F85377f3b4b5097c32bc845e51e17%2F186071607-20250208-111044.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1688+0+873/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fac%2F3c%2F85377f3b4b5097c32bc845e51e17%2F186071607-20250208-111044.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1688+0+873/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fac%2F3c%2F85377f3b4b5097c32bc845e51e17%2F186071607-20250208-111044.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x1688+0+873/resize/1800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.a