25px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3300x1856+0+939/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fef%2F89%2F0d6ad1d742b48c6ea813208c3ad8%2F186071607-the-beat-of-the-street-liz-daino-photography.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3300x1856+0+939/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fef%2F89%2F0d6ad1d742b48c6ea813208c3ad8%2F186071607-the-beat-of-the-street-liz-daino-photography.jpg" class="img" alt="A second line wedding parade in New Orleans. " loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 A second line wedding parade in New Orleans.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Liz Daino                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;A second line wedding parade is a tradition in New Orleans where the newly married couple celebrate through the streets with their guests, accompanied by a brass band. Liz Daino was able to capture one of those magical moments. The 36-year-old says it felt as if everything was aligned: the music, the movement and the light for the picture. Daino said that even the sun flare illuminates the energy and soul of the celebration — a visual love letter to the city that is unapologetically alive. "With the 20th anniversary of Hurricane Katrina approaching, this image feels especially powerful. It reminds me how resilient and vibrant this city remains," Daino said. To her, it is a reminder that joy doesn't always stand still; sometimes it marches.&lt;/p&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Daino's tip: &lt;/strong&gt;"Forget perfection — chase presence. Know your light, anticipate the moment before it happens, and then let the emotion lead. Oh, and never underestimate the power of good shoes, especially in a city where your best shot might require a little dancing."&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-82620" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 4284;         --source-height: 2410;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4284x2410+0+1354/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F96%2F69%2Fb3ba61d84b85aadd1c08f9f6963d%2F186071607-img-2921.jpeg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4284x2410+0+1354/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F96%2F69%2Fb3ba61d84b85aadd1c08f9f6963d%2F186071607-img-2921.jpeg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4284x2410+0+1354/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F96%2F69%2Fb3ba61d84b85aadd1c08f9f6963d%2F186071607-img-2921.jpeg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4284x2410+0+1354/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F96%2F69%2Fb3ba61d84b85aadd1c08f9f6963d%2F186071607-img-2921.jpeg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4284x2410+0+1354/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F96%2F69%2Fb3ba61d84b85aadd1c08f9f6963d%2F186071607-img-2921.jpeg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dim